<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>403 - 访问被拒绝</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div class="text-center p-10 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-md w-full">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-orange-500 m-0">403</h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 my-5">访问被拒绝</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">很抱歉，您没有权限访问此页面。如果您认为这是一个错误，请联系网站管理员。</p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-blue-500 text-white no-underline rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-300">返回首页</a>
            <button onclick="history.back()" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-gray-500 text-white no-underline rounded hover:bg-gray-600 transition duration-300">返回上一页</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
